Package: move2imu
Type: Package
Title: Handling Bursted IMU Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bart", "Kranstauber", , "b.kranstauber@uva.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8303-780X")),
    person("Finn", "Roberts", , "froberts@ab.mpg.de", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Standardized vector representation of bursted
    inertial measurement unit (IMU) data collected by animal tracking
    devices, including accelerometer, magnetometer, and gyroscope sensors.
    Extract and manipulate IMU data from move2 objects and tracking data stored
    in Movebank.
